## §2 — ARQUITETURA DO SISTEMA

### Topologia

```text
Root (pnpm workspace)
├─ Frontend (Astro 6 · static)
│   ├─ src/pages/            → index, login, signup, upgrade, success, legal
│   ├─ src/components/       → AstroChatInterface.astro (SSE streaming)
│   └─ public/               → assets, SVG banners
│
└─ Backend (Express · Node 22+)
    ├─ src/server.js          → Core API (único arquivo de servidor)
    ├─ src/lib/redis.js       → Redis real (prod) | mock in-memory (dev)
    ├─ src/services/ledger.js → Ledger soberano de tokens (Redis List)
    └─ src/utils/billing.js   → Estimativa de consumo via SSE chunks
```

### Fluxo de chat

```text
1. POST /api/chat (Bearer JWT)
2. authenticateToken → createUserRateLimit → checkQuota
3. System prompt do cache de memória (boot-time, não I/O por request)
4. Proxy Venice AI com AbortController (timeout: VENICE_TIMEOUT_MS)
5. SSE pipe → cliente (TextDecoder reutilizado, reader.releaseLock no finally)
6. ledgerService.addEntry (assíncrono, não bloqueia resposta)
```

### Fluxo de pagamento

```text
POST /api/flowpay/create-charge
  → FlowPay API (timeout 10s) → checkoutUrl
    → Usuário paga em flowpay.cash
      → FlowPay → Nexus → POST /webhooks/flowpay (X-Nexus-Signature)
        → HMAC-SHA256 timingSafeEqual
          → pipeline Redis: tier:{userId} = "pro"
            → ledger: +FLOWPAY_CREDITS_ON_PURCHASE tokens (PURCHASE)
```

### Redis keys

```text
tier:{userId}       → "free" | "pro"
limit:{userId}      → tokens/dia (padrão: 100)
password:{userId}   → bcrypt hash
ledger:{userId}     → Redis List, LIFO, ltrim a 1000 entradas
```

---

## §3 — API REFERENCE

**Base URL dev:** `http://localhost:3001`  
**Auth:** `Authorization: Bearer <JWT>`  
**Body limit:** 64kb  

| Método | Rota | Auth | Descrição |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/chat` | ✅ | Proxy Venice AI (SSE stream) |
| GET | `/api/models` | ✅ | Lista modelos Venice (timeout 10s) |
| GET | `/api/usage` | ✅ | Quota diária do usuário |
| GET | `/api/ledger` | ✅ | Extrato + saldo do ledger |
| POST | `/api/auth/signup` | ❌ | Cadastro (rate: 10/15min) |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | ❌ | Login timing-safe (rate: 10/15min) |
| POST | `/api/flowpay/create-charge` | ✅ | Criar cobrança FlowPay |
| POST | `/webhooks/flowpay` | HMAC | Consumer Nexus (não chamar diretamente) |
| GET | `/health` | ❌ | Status + uptime |

**Schema `/api/chat` body (Zod):**
```json
{
  "messages": [{ "role": "user|system|assistant", "content": "1–32000 chars" }],
  "model": "string (opcional)",
  "stream": true,
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "enableWebSearch": false
}
```

